There are a lot of misconceptions about what a BossBabe is… so we decided to ask YOU. If you’re an ambitious woman with big dreams, we’d love to support you in turning them into a reality.

Our signature membership, The Société, is now open for enrollment and we’re ready to show you what a REAL community looks like. Head to the link in our bio for more info or to join.

node.text:
From 0 followers to household name, here’s exactly what I did: ⬇️

Let’s first bust two myths you might’ve heard floating around:

Myth #1: Building a successful business is easy…

Myth #2: There’s one single thing you can do to become successful…

Firstly, it isn’t easy - it’s more like a roller coaster that you get on daily.  🎢

But it is seriously worth it. Kinda the same as ANYTHING worth having right?

Secondly, there isn’t one secret funnel or social media trick that is going to turn your idea into a successful business overnight…

However, there is a step-by-step process that almost any business type, in any industry, can follow. This process will take you from the baby idea stage, to having an incredibly successful, 6, 7 or 8+ figure business.

Me and my business partner, Danielle, created this process after a combined decade in multiple businesses, and after mentoring over 120,000 students ourselves.

We realized that there are six steps that you can follow in a linear fashion, to create a successful business. Think of it as your Satellite Navigation (Tesla style) to profit. 💸

So, we took these steps and built an entire membership platform around them, to take the guesswork out of the process. We call it: The Société.

Right now, doors are open to The Société and members who join us right now (for less than the cost of a latte per day!) are going to get access to a bundle of bonuses on top of their membership.

Ready to stop driving in circles and plug into a system that actually works? Hit the link in our bio below to join us!

node.text:
The July Masterclass is HERE! ✨⁠⁣
⁣
We are SO excited to share @itskrista and @lindseysimcik exclusive Masterclass with you on How To Develop, Launch & Record A Successful Podcast! 🎙️⁣
⁣
Krista and Lindsey are the creators and hosts of the widely successful @almost30podcast, which has been named Top Health Podcast and Top Spirituality Podcast by iHeartRadio and has also been featured in Forbes, Entrepreneur, Coveteur, Girlboss, The Hollywood Reporter, and Authority Magazine.⁣
⁣
In their own words, “Podcasting completely changed our lives — it gave us a platform to have our voices heard, connect with millions of people around the world, and build a successful business doing what we love every day.”⁣
⁣
Now, Krista and Lindsey have put together everything they’ve learned to help you build the podcast, brand, and business you’ve always dreamed of EXCLUSIVELY in The Société.⁣
⁣
Link in bio to check out The Société and get access to this Masterclass! ⬆️

node.title: Podcast Masterclass with Krista Williams & Lindsey Simcik

node.text:
Real influence is built through sharing UNIQUE content.

That’s why we created The Content Masterclass...to teach you how to STAND OUT so you don’t end up just fitting in.

This is perfect for you if…

✅ You’re ready for a brand new content strategy and want to learn exactly how you can use your own uniqueness to truly build influence and stand out.

✅ You don’t know WHAT content to post never mind HOW to create it, and want to get more intentional and purposeful with what you put out online

✅ You’re camera shy, and want to learn how to increase your confidence so you’re much more comfortable in front of it

✅ You want a feed that’s aesthetically pleasing like other entrepreneurs' and influencers' online, where the fonts and colours are consistent and visually reflect you and your business/brand but don’t know where to start

✅ You post from time-to-time but when you do, it’s to crickets - you want to learn the kind of content that’s actually going to get you engagement and increase your reach

✅ You don’t have any fancy equipment, but you do have a smartphone, and want to learn how to use it to capture photos and videos that look legit

✅ You’re in a permanent state of post paralysis because you don’t have a bank of content to pull from - you want to learn how to batch so you can create quickly, easily and always have plenty of choice

✅ You want to learn how to edit like a pro, so that you can elevate your content and uplevel your feed so it looks not just cute, but cohesive too

...because in this course, I’ll be spilling ALL of our content creation and marketing secrets, and you can access it this weekend ONLY for $97 instead of $500 (saving 80%!). 🤯

Click our link in bio to sign up at the discounted price before our sale ends on Monday at midnight!

node.title: Real influence doesn’t come from cookie cutter captions and content.

node.text:
Social media is changing. 

The kind of content that used to get engagement, a.k.a. likes, comments, shares and saves just isn’t hitting the mark anymore. 🤷‍♀️

The algorithm is giving favor to what keeps people on the platform…

...which means static images are out, and moving video like Reels and IGTVs are in.

But… that’s not the kind of content that’s super easy to produce if you’re not a professional, right?

And so you’ve probably noticed a huge drop in your engagement recently...

...but not to worry.

With 2.8M+ on Instagram, 232K+ on Facebook, 1.3M+ monthly views on Pinterest and 1M+ views on YouTube I think it’s safe to say that at BossBabe we know what works and what doesn’t when it comes to content creation and marketing, and we have a crazy amazing deal on a course, through which we teach you all we know. 😉

In The Content Masterclass, you'll get: 
📸7x modules of 16x videos designed with your content creation game in mind 
📸@iamnatalie's favorite presets for a professional finish in post-production 
📸BossBabe’s content calendar so you know EXACTLY what to post and when to attract an audience and drive traffic to make sales 
📸An exclusive video on how to monetize your content and grow your Instagram account 

Did we mention that all of this is $97 THIS WEEKEND ONLY?! That's right...over $2,600 worth of content for just $97.  What are you waiting for?! Link in bio!

node.text:
We’re so excited to have @goodamerican CEO and Co-founder, Emma Grede @emmagrede 👑, join us on the BossBabe Instagram to share the real behind-the-scenes of creating such a meaningful brand that truly promotes inclusivity and diversity beyond their campaigns.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Emma is lifting the lid on what it took to build a multi-million dollar fashion brand in an already “saturated” denim industry. 💸⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
If you dream of having your own product-based business, then you’re in luck. Emma is delivering PURE value with mindset shifts and tangible actions that you can start implementing right away! 🙌⁣⁣⁣
⁣
🎙 Make sure to tune in to Emma's episode on #TheBossBabePodcast. Search for "The BossBabe Podcast Episode 98" on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, or anywhere you listen to podcasts.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣

node.title: How To Break Into a Saturated Market w/ Emma Grede, CEO of Good American

It’s LAUNCH DAY! 🎉✨ Today, we launched Online Launch School: a 12-week program designed to take the guesswork out of online launches, whether you’re looking to start a business or scale one.⁣
⁣
Online Launch School is for you if you’re ready to have the biggest cash injection in your business that you’ve ever had, through learning how to launch effectively.⁣
⁣
This is our second course at BossBabe and if you were part of our first (IGA), you’ll know that we’re queens of overdelivering. That’s exactly what we’re bringing you this time around, too.⁣
⁣
If you join us within the next 14 days, here’s what bonuses you’re going to get:⁣
⁣
➡️ You’ll save $1,000 OFF your enrollment cost!⁣
➡️ Full access to Online Launch School (content valued at $4,997!)⁣
➡️ Bonus FB community with me, Danielle, team BossBabe & your OLS classmates, incl 6 x Q&A calls & a chance to get featured on BossBabe IG ($3,000 value)⁣
➡️ Done for you launch success planner ($97 value)⁣
➡️ 1 x free ticket to the BossBabe Online Launch Summit in October (virtual!) ($497 value)⁣
⁣
and the BEST bonus of all:⁣
⁣
➡️ Done for you funnel & copy bundle… aka pages of email sequence copy ready for you to plug and play, as well as ClickFunnels templates already designed for you. This comes with video tutorials, so even if you’ve never seen a funnel before, you’ll be able to implement with ease. This bundle alone is valued at $1497!⁣
⁣
All of this is valued at $10,088, but if you join us within the next 14 days, you’ll get full access for $997. ⚡️ Who’s in already?! We’re SO excited! Link in bio to join OLS now. ✨⁣
⁣
Or you can sign up for OLS here: https://bossbabe.com/join-ols⁣
⁣
Watch the webinar replay here: https://bossbabe.com/the-launch-formula⁣
⁣
Use code BOSSBABE to get 15% off your next purchase with @organifi: bossbabe.online/organifi

node.text:
[NEW PODCAST EPISODE 🎙️] Do you want to know the one thing that BossBabe’s co-founders, @iamnatalie and @daniellecanty, credit to the success of their business relationship? One word: communication.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Join us in this episode on The BossBabe Podcast as we take you behind-the-scenes of what it really looks like to be in a business relationship with your best friend and how to cultivate a thriving partnership.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
We'll cover:⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
✔️ How Natalie and Danielle use communication to cultivate a thriving business relationship⁣⁣⁣
✔️ The real behind-the-scenes of being Biz Besties while living and working together ⁣⁣⁣⁣
✔️ How Natalie and Danielle navigated being business partners from different parts of the world ⁣⁣⁣⁣
✔️ How things have changed since Danielle’s big move to join Natalie in Los Angeles⁣⁣⁣
✔️ Why over-communication is key, especially for remote teams based in different locations⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
🎙️To hear the full episode, search for "The BossBabe Podcast" on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, or anywhere you listen to podcasts.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
#bossbabe #thebossbabepodcast #thebossbabesociete #bossbabe #sponsored

Wanna meet your new favorite community of boss babes?! ✨⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
We’re @iamnatalie and @daniellecanty: the business besties behind the global brand BossBabe – one of the fastest growing online communities of ambitious women and female entrepreneurs. 👑⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
We’ve created the MOST supportive, high-vibe, value-driven community of ladies on the internet… and it’s quickly become THE place for us “bossy” women to make moves and accomplish our big goals. ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
So whether you’ve got a pre-start or ready to scale business, The Société is the best place to get the accountability, support, and resources required to succeed BIG. ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
We’ve supported thousands of women to build their businesses through The Société and we’d love to help you do the same. ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Come tap into our proven roadmap, step-by-step action plans, tons of daily accountability, and an incredible group of business besties inside The Société… ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Oh and did we mention it’s just about $1 per day to become a member. 👏👏⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Click the LINK IN OUR BIO or visit bossbabe.com/membership to dive into our community and get started whilst doors are open.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 31, 2021 tagging @iamnatalie. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Natalie Ellis @iamnatalie 6 things I wish I knew sooner (a thread)'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Natalie Ellis @iamnatalie 1. Their feelings aren't your fault, or your responsibility. Showing up with kindness and empathy is important, but remember you are not responsible for how they react or feel. Continue to advocate for yourself, speak your truth and stand in your boundaries. Some people will be unable to handle that, but you'll naturally call and curate the right people in your life... and that's so much more fulfilling.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 31, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Natalie Ellis @iamnatalie 2. The depth of your relationship will reflect the depth you have within yourself. If you're lacking depth in a relationship, consider how much of it you have in your relationship to yourself. As you find new levels and layers within yourself you'll naturally find that with others too.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Natalie Ellis @iamnatalie 3. Loyalty to yourself comes above all else. Be loyal to yourself above anything or anyone else. That's how you'll attract the relationships, career and mindset that you're looking for. When you're disloyal to yourself, you follow the paths you think you *should* follow, or if your loyalty to a job or relationship ranks higher than your own, you'l settle for something that feels toxic or out of alignment.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Natalie Ellis @iamnatalie 4. People will project their own shit onto you, stay strong. There's a big difference between receiving feedback and being projected onto. You showing up in your fullest expression and confidence is going to trigger the fuck out of people who haven't unlocked that for themselves yet. Stay strong and remember who you are.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Natalie Ellis @iamnatalie 5. Health is your most important asset, treat it that way. We often mistake time as our most important asset, but time is nothing without health. Remember that the people you surround yourself with and the content you consume also contribute to the health of your mind. Make time to eat well, workout, set your boundaries and do your routines.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 31, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Natalie Ellis @iamnatalie 6. Money might make you happy, but it won't keep you happy. Being in a place where you're not stressed about paying your bills is incredibly important, but remember that money isn't everything. The quality of your relationships, the level of fulfillment you have and the deeper you know yourself will contribute way more to your happiness.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Perfection is a myth. Procrastination is real. Be careful you're not using one to feed the other. @bossbabe.inc'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'B BOSSBABE @bossbabe.inc 8 uncomfortable truths that we all need to hear (a thread)'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'B BOSSB BOSSBABE @bossbabe.inc 1. If you keep moving from toxic situation or relationship... to toxic situation or relationship, it might be time to look inward.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'BOSSBABE @bossbabe.inc B 2. Real talk: you might find yourself constantly second guessing a decision you made or situation that you're in... and it might not actually be because something needs to change. You might be second guessing it because you don't truly believe that you deserve it.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'BO BOSSBABE @bossbabe.inc 3. Decisions made from a place of burnout are probably not going to be great long-term decisions. Before committing to something, check in with yourself and ask if you're doing it because you're tired, burnt out and need a break. If the answer is yes, address the root cause versus putting a band-aid on it.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'BOSSBABE @bossbabe.inc BO 4. If you're an influencer, creator or entrepreneur with an audience... never forget that you're where you are right now because of your audience. Don't make the mistake of getting too big for your audience, it's one you'll struggle to come back from.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'BO BOSSBABE @bossbabe.inc 5. Look at ROI (return on investment) as more than just financial. You're going to lose time and money with some of the decisions you make if you're really pushing yourself out of your comfort zone in the name of growth. What did you learn in the process? What mistakes will you avoid next time?'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'BOSSBABE @bossbabe.inc BO 6. If you're always right, chances are that you're actually not always right. You're just finding ways to shut out alternative views points or blind spots. Recognize when you're putting yourself in a bubble to protect your ego.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'BO BOSSBABE @bossbabe.inc Striving for balance is going to leave you feeling like a failure, and filled with guilt, in one area at all times. Recognize that balance doesn't exist and each season of your life will call for a new version of harmony. Go into it eyes wide open, knowing what you can and can't prioritize, and be okay with that.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'B BOSSBABE @bossbabe.inc 8. If you want to be a good leader, you need to let go of blaming anyone but yourself. If you notice a leader or manager who is constantly olamn everyone but themselves, take it as a big red flag.'.

Photo by BossBabe™ | Watch IG Stories! on July 30, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'YOU VIBE ON A WHOLE DIFFERENT LEVEL WHEN YOU COMMIT TO YOURSELF, TAKE CONSISTENT ACTION, AND STAY IN YOUR LANE. @bossbabe.inc'.

node.text:
Real talk: you don’t need to go into debt to build a business… ❌

Listen, whether it’s the debt of a college education or a five figure mastermind…

You 👏 don’t 👏 need 👏 it 👏 to 👏 build 👏 a 👏 successful 👏 business.

Can I say that louder for the people in the back?!

Grab a domain name, register your social handle and secure a Société membership… spending less than a latte a day, and you’ve got everything you need to build a successful 6 or 7+ figure business.

I’m not joking.

I’ve done it, multiple times, and so have thousands of the people we’ve mentored.

Within The Société, we’ve brought together some of THE most successful 7, 8 and 9 figure entrepreneurs in the WORLD, to share with you their secrets for building their businesses.

Like @jamiekernlima, who took her business from her bedroom to selling to L’Oreal for $1.2B. Yes, the B stands for BILLION.

Jamie, and so many other entrepreneurs like her, opened up their homes so we could come in behind the scenes and ask all the questions we know you’re dying to know the answers to.

Other entrepreneurs have been there, done that, got the t-shirt, MBA, multiple failures and eventually massive successes…

So that they could come back and share with you everything they learned along the way.

The best shortcut to your success is to learn from people who are where YOU want to be.

Ready to join us? Link in bio to secure your spot inside The Société. ⬆️
